      <p>Many adults in the UK are eligible for up to £20,000 per year in student finance — and don’t even know it. We support learners aged 21–60 who haven’t completed a university degree. If you're working part-time, on benefits, or earning under £30,000, we can help you apply to university and change your future.</p>
