        <div class="section-title">📋 Entry Requirements</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Age: 21 to 60</li>
          <li>B1 level English or above</li>
          <li>British Citizen, Settled Status, or Leave to Remain</li>
          <li>No formal qualifications required</li>
          <li>Lived in the UK for 3+ years</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section>
        <div class="section-title">🗂️ Documents Needed</div>
