      <div class="section-title">📚 Courses and Study Structure</div>
      <p>We offer flexible pathways to a recognised UK degree. All our programs are structured to support mature learners and fit around work or family life.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Pathway 1:</strong> 1-Year Foundation + 3-Year Bachelor’s Degree</li>
        <li><strong>Pathway 2:</strong> 2-Year Foundation + 2-Year Top-Up to Bachelor’s Degree</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Available Subjects:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Business and Business Management</li>
        <li>Health and Social Care</li>
        <li>Law</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Study Days:</strong> 1 day/week (9–5pm) or 2 shorter days (10–12 or 6–8pm).</p>
    </section>

